title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Miscellaneous Articles Of Base Metal
description: Imports Intra Eu - Miscellaneous Articles Of Base Metal in the United Kingdom increased to 99.49 GBP Million in September from 94.06 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Miscellaneous Articles Of Base in the United Kingdom averaged 63.69 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 126.21 GBP Million in January of 2022 and a record low of 7 GBP Million in March of 2015. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Miscellaneous Articles of B.
